    <description>Matrix-style Sales Outlook — pipeline pacing by channel record type for the current fiscal year. Rows = channel RT (TV-Linear, Digital, Radio-Linear, etc.); columns = Budget, TY$, Forecast, Pending, FC to Budget. LY$ and % Change deferred until prior-year actuals are linkable to Opportunity.</description>
